  "description": "An even more detailed experience with quadruple-resolution textures!",
  "body": "<center>\n\t<img style=\"width: 1142px;\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/wordmarks/outlined/cracked/f64_wordmark.png\">\n\t<h1>The go-to 64x resource pack for Minecraft.</h1>\n\t<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft-bedrock/addons/faithful-64x-bedrock\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/bedrock_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Get the Bedrock pack here\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n</center>\n<hr>\n<p>\n    The logical next step in upscaling Minecraft textures. Just like Faithful 32x, this pack is based on the default art—masterfully remade in quadruple \n\tthe resolution and adding just the right amount of extra detail for the perfect vanilla-style Minecraft experience. \n\t<br><br>\n    By basing its textures directly on its 32x counterparts, it achieves great consistency between packs and is always improving in quality. \\\n\tIf you're into detailed resource packs but still want that vanilla feel, this pack is for you!\n\n</p>\n<center>\n\t<a href=\"https://discord.gg/sN9YRQbBv7\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img style=\"width: 1142px;\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/discord_button.png\" alt=\"Discord Server\">\n\t</a>\n  <br><br>\n\t<a href=\"https://faithfulpack.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img style=\"width: 1142px;\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/website_button.png\" alt=\"Website\">\n\t</a>\n</center>\n<hr>\n<center><h2>Additional Information:</h2></center>\n<p>\n\tIf you have any feedback, want to report a bug, or generally need help,\n\tjoin our <a href=\"https://discord.gg/sN9YRQbBv7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Discord</a> server above, make a\n\t<a href=\"https://github.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Faithful-64x-Java/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub issue</a>,\n\tor comment below. For any commercial or distribution-related questions, refer to our\n\t<a href=\"http://faithfulpack.net/license\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">license</a>.\n\t<br><br>\n\tAll textures and add-ons are provided by contributors volunteering in their free time.\n\tAnyone can submit textures through our Discord server linked above, or make an\n\t<a href=\"http://faithfulpack.net/addons\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">add-on</a>\n\tto officially list on our website. Before you begin, make sure to read our\n\t<a href=\"https://docs.faithfulpack.net/pages/textures/f64-texturing-guidelines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">texturing guidelines</a>\n\twhich precisely outline the art style of the pack.\n\t<br><br>\n\tEach pack has listings on our <a href=\"faithfulpack.net\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">website</a>,\n\t<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/faithful_resource_pack/projects\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CurseForge</a>,\n\t<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/member/faithful_resource_pack/submissions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Planet Minecraft</a>,\n\tand <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Faithful-Resource-Pack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Modrinth</a>,\n\tand some packs are additionally listed on <a href=\"https://mcpedl.com/user/faithful-resource-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MCPEDL</a>\n\tand the <a href=\"https://www.minecraftforum.net/members/Faithful_Resource_Pack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Minecraft Forums</a>.\n\t<strong>Downloads from any other sites are unofficial, unsupported and could be dangerous!</strong>\n\tRemember to stay safe on the internet.\n</p>\n<hr>\n<center><h2>Our Other Projects:</h2></center>\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">\n\t<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/faithful-32x\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/f32_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Faithful 32x\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n\t<br><br>\n\t<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/classic-faithful-32x-programmer-art\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/cf32_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Classic Faithful 32x\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n\t<br><br>\n\t<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/classic-faithful-32x-jappa\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/cf32j_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Classic Faithful 32x Jappa\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n\t<br><br>\n\t<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/classic-faithful-64x\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/cf64j_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Classic Faithful 64x Jappa\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n</div>",
